        "story-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Where Luxury Meets Healing",
            "size": "2xl"
          }
        },
        "story-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Velvet Touch was born from a simple belief: that self-care shouldn't feel like a luxury reserved for special occasions. Founded by Elena Vasquez in Manhattan's West Village, the spa was designed to be a sanctuary — a place where everyday stress dissolves the moment you walk through the door.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        },
        "story-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What began as a single treatment room has grown into a full-service day spa with a team of ten licensed therapists. But the philosophy hasn't changed: listen first, treat with intention, and never rush the experience.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["story-eyebrow", "story-heading", "story-text-1", "story-text-2"]
